If regular click does not work for you can use the alternatice way
of having Actions class click method

*** Upload Documents ***
In order to upload documents using selenium we simply do sendKeys(file path)

If sendKeys method does not work, you can use Robot class
Robot class(gives us opportunity to handle with windows based popups)

*** JavaScriptExecuter ***
-it is a library in selenium which can be executed in different programing language
(java, c#,python etc.)

-JSExecuter is an interface

*** Actions which can ber perform by using JSExecuter ***

-Click on the element ---------------------- js.executeScript("arguments[0].click()",logInButton);
-Scroll through the page ------------------- js.executeScript("window.scrollBy(0,500)");
-Refresh the page
-Highlight an element ---------------------- js.executeScript("arguments[0].style.backgroundColor = 'red'",email);
-Scrollto a specific element --------------- js.executeScript("arguments[0].scrollIntoView(true)",backToTopButton);
-Open a new tab ---------------------------- js.executeScript("window.open();"); --> opens a blank tab
                                             js.executeScript("window.open('https://www.amazon.com/');");
